Titolo: Avadon: The Black Fortress

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: Avadon: The Black Fortress is a single-player role-playing video game developed by Spiderweb Software. It is the first game in the Avadon trilogy. The game was released for Mac OS X in February 2011, and for Microsoft Windows in May. Version for the iPad was released on June 18. It was later released for Android and Linux, and included in the Humble Bundle for Android 2.

